        "description": "## Add School\n\nAdds a new school to the system.\n\n### Request Body\n\n| Field | Type | Description |\n|-------|------|-------------|\n| `name` | string | The name of the school (e.g., \"Slate School\") |\n| `address` | string | The physical address or city of the school (e.g., \"Jagtial\") |\n| `latitude` | number | The geographic latitude coordinate of the school location |\n| `longitude` | number | The geographic longitude coordinate of the school location |\n\n### Response\n\nReturns a `201 Created` status on success with a confirmation message and the created school object, including its assigned `id`.\n\n**Example Response:**\n```json\n{\n  \"message\": \"School added successfully\",\n  \"school\": {\n    \"name\": \"Slate School\",\n    \"address\": \"Jagtial\",\n    \"latitude\": 18.8,\n    \"longitude\": 79.15,\n    \"id\": 3\n  }\n}\n```"
