        "description": "## List Schools\n\nRetrieves a list of schools sorted by proximity to a given geographic location. Provide latitude and longitude coordinates as query parameters, and the API returns all schools along with their calculated distance from the specified point.\n\n---\n\n## Query Parameters\n\n| Parameter | Type | Required | Description |\n| --- | --- | --- | --- |\n| `latitude` | number | ✅ Yes | The latitude coordinate of the reference location (e.g. `17.3850`) |\n| `longitude` | number | ✅ Yes | The longitude coordinate of the reference location (e.g. `78.4867`) |\n\n---\n\n## Sample Response\n\n**Status:** `200 OK`\n\n``` json\n[\n  {\n    \"id\": 1,\n    \"name\": \"Indo American School\",\n    \"address\": \"hyderabad\",\n    \"latitude\": 17.4,\n    \"longitude\": 78.36,\n    \"distance\": \"13.55 km\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"id\": 2,\n    \"name\": \"ABC School\",\n    \"address\": \"Kamareddy\",\n    \"latitude\": 18.31,\n    \"longitude\": 79.15,\n    \"distance\": \"124.53 km\"\n  }\n]\n\n ```\n\n### Response Fields\n\n| Field | Type | Description |\n| --- | --- | --- |\n| `id` | integer | Unique identifier of the school |\n| `name` | string | Name of the school |\n| `address` | string | Address or city where the school is located |\n| `latitude` | number | Latitude coordinate of the school |\n| `longitude` | number | Longitude coordinate of the school |\n| `distance` | string | Calculated distance from the provided coordinates to the school (e.g. `\"13.55 km\"`) |"
      },
